@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
[*] --> Cancelled
Cancelled --> Delivered : update
Cancelled : entry / log insurance
Delivered --> Approved : update
Approved --> Archived : submit
Archived --> Reviewed : reject
Reviewed --> Processing : update
Delivered --> Processing : revert
Processing --> [*]
@enduml